text.content: I wonder, wonder wonder  Why your eyes they wonder?

I wonder, wonder wonder  About the spell that you are under  Tell me its some hocus pocus  Made to lose your focus  I wonder why the cold kiss and you think I wouldn't notice    [Bridge]  You don't love me like you say you do  You don't want me the way that I want you  You don't love me like you say you do (you do) you do    [Chorus: x2]  Can I get me some satisfaction [Repeat: x3]  That's all I'm asking you, you, of you  Give me the magic pass, that's all I ask of you    I wonder if it's over, middle of October  I don't know why in autumn, she keeps giving a cold shoulder  She knows how much I love her don't know what I could have told her  I wonder why she makes me think I didn't even know her    [Bridge]    Why don't you give me (give me give me give me give me your love)  Give me your love (give me give me give me your love  Is that too much to ask you can I  Get some satisfaction from you    [Bridge]    [Chorus: Repeats]
